*** fanfictionnet_ff_proxy: an experimental "proxy" for fanfiction.net ***
/!\ Very hacky/buggy code - DO NOT USE.

This code (with the included very hacky patch for FanFicFare) permit a manual bypass of the CloudFare captcha for FanFiction.net
It drive Firefox through Selenium.

** USAGE **
* Run python3 ./ff_content.py
* When you see "INFO root Will listen on port 8888", the code is initialized
* To use: echo https://www.fanfiction.net/s/10273521/1/Songbird |nc 127.0.0.1 8888
--> You should get back the source code of this URL and the socket will be disconnected

/!\ If you see "Complete the captcha then press enter", switch to the Firefox window and do the captcha.
¨¨    Press Enter when you're done, the page will reload and you should see the source code of the URL you request

Do this a first time so cookie.json is initialized
Control+C quit the browser, do it twice to quit the software
